snippet.title: Slendrina Must Die: The Asylum
snippet.description:
Buy Me A Cup Of Coffee ? You can do that here https://gogetfunding.com/one-cup-of-coffee-so-i-can-work-more-easily/
Thanks.

Android Download: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.PoisonGames.SlendrinaMustDieTheAsylum

PC Download: http://gamejolt.com/games/SlendrinaMustDieTheAsylum/262370

Slendrina Must Die is back in a new scary adventure! The Asylum!

She is much more angry then usual. Be careful, she is protecting something.
Also, watch out for Slendrinas Mother! She is one old evil witch !

Find 8 Old Medical Books in the Abandoned Asylum.

Features:
- Awesome 3D Graphics
- Easy Controls
- Well known Poison Games Gameplay
- Scary Game with Firearms!

* Three weapons:
- Gun
- MP5
- Shotgun

Game is based on Slendrina: Asylum
